Debug")i=bf("Invert Horizontal Rotation")j=bf("Invert Vertical Rotation")k=bf("Aim Mode")l=bf("Requires Is Occupied?")m=bg("Horizontal Pivot Type")n=bg("Vertical Pivot Type")o=bg("Angle Units")p=bg("Horizontal Max Angle (Robotic Only)")q=bg("Horizontal Min Angle (Robotic Only)")r=bg("Vertical Max Angle (Robotic Only)")s=bg("Vertical Min Angle (Robotic Only)")t=bg("Missile Count")u=bg("Time Between Missiles (s)")v=bg("Min Mass")w=bg("Max Mass")x=bg("Min Y")y=bg("Max Y")z=bg("Yaw Threshold")A=bg("Pitch Threshold")B=bg("Min Distance")C=bg("Max Distance")D=bn.pi*2 function E(F,G,H,I)return bh(H-F,I-G)/D end function J(H,I,F,G)return bn.sqrt((F-H)^2+(G-I)^2)end function K()L=1 if o==1 then L=D elseif o==2 then L=400 elseif o==3 then L=360 end p=M(p/L/4)q=M(q/L/4)r=M(r/L/4)s=M(s/L/4)z=M(z/L)A=M(A/L)end function onTick()if not b then K()b=bq end c=c+1 if e<t then N=bo.getBool(1)if not l or l and N then O=bi(10)if w==0 or O>=v and O<=w then P=bi(2)if P>=x and P<=y then Q=bi(7)R=bi(9)S=bi(1)T=bi(3)U=J(Q,R,S,T)if U>=B and U<=C+300 then V=bi(8)W=bi(4)X=bi(5)Y=bi(6)Z=E(S,T,Q,R)-W f=0 g=0 if m==0 or m==1 then bb=4 if i then bb=-4 end f=M(bc(bn.bd(Z,q,p)*bb,-1,1))end if n==0 or n==1 then bb=4 if j then bb=-4 end g=M(bn.bd(bh((P-V)/U)/D,s,r)*bb)end if bj(X*4-f)<=z then if bj(Y*4-g)<=A then if d==0 or c-d>=u*60 then if U<C then e=e+1 bm.setBool(e,bq)d=c end end end end end end end end end bk(1,f)bk(2,g)end function onDraw()if h then if X then if bj(X*4-f)<=z then bl(0,0,"Y yaw thrsh: "..(bs):format(z)..br..(bs):format(bj(X*4-f)))else bl(0,0,"X yaw thrsh: "..(bs):format(z)..br..(bs):format(bj(X*4-f)))end else bl(0,0,"horizontal_rot doesnt exist")end if Y then if bj(Y*4-g)<=A then bl(0,10,"Y pitch thrsh: "..(bs):format(A)..bt..(bs):format(bj(Y*4-g)))else bl(0,10,"X pitch thrsh: "..(bs):format(A)..bt..(bs):format(bj(Y*4-g)))end else bl(0,10,"vertical_rot doesnt exist")end if not l or l and N then bl(0,20,"occupied status ready!")end end end function bn.bd(be,min,max)return max<be and max or min>be and min or be end function M(be)return be~=be and 0 or be end function bc(be,min,max)return(be-min)/(max-min)%1*(max-min)+min end
